  * [8ed7848] remove unused DEBIAN_VERSION vars in rules file
  * [9959bd5] DEB_HOST_GNU_TYPE, DEB_BUILD_GNU_TYPE and DEB_BUILD_ARCH are
    defined by cdbs too
  * [9f6c088] Fix misalignments in --help command line

