    - update debian/guacharo.preinst
  * update guacharo menu section - use "Applications/Network/Communication"
    (Closes: 444903)
    - update debian/guacharo.menu
  * don't try to install debian/tmp/usr/lib/guacharo/defaults/isp as its not
    shipped by make install anymore
    - update debian/guacharo.install

